name: Auto Icon  (+69k Icons)
description:
Auto Icon is the largest Icon Library for UI Designers.

Get access to most popular icon collection of over 69,000 SVG Icons, Including 17,000 Free and 52,000 Premium Icons


Search by Icon name, and Just Drag & Drop to your design :).


Some of the most popular icon collections are:

  • Material UI
  • Material Design
  • Font Awesome
  • Bootstrap Icon
  • Feather Icons
  • Ionicons
  • Plus 66 more Icons Packs


These vector Icons are Simple, high-quality designs & Customizable. You can easily change the size, color, etc.


In Order to Access Premium Icons you need to purchase a license. You can find more details on the website: https://uxplugins.com/auto-icon
